{"tid":1764872,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【抗暴之戰】茂名勇武抗爭4日獲勝 黨委書記宣佈：永不建火葬場","createTime":"2019-12-01T12:18:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T12:59:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0a8de2552eb9bb9f2dfd6003170768e0053caaeb","tid":1764872,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:18:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191201/60330194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191201%2F60330194&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=c9136fcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191201%2F60330194&h=61c6573e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20191201/60330194</a><br />\n<br />\n【抗暴之戰】茂名勇武抗爭4日獲勝 黨委書記宣佈：永不建火葬場<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191201/large/1575182755_6508.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191201%2Flarge%2F1575182755_6508.jpg&h=fc3fd59e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港正式輸給廣東茂名文樓鎮，當地市民不滿政府以興建人文生態園為名徵地，實際建設火葬場，自上周四起展開大規模示威，「就好像你們香港，遍地開花。」但不同於香港，抗爭在短短4天內落幕。今天，有現場影片顯示，文樓鎮黨委書記李偉華宣佈，永遠不在文樓鎮建火葬場。<br />\n<br />\n片中可見，李偉華率領一眾官員及律師會見民眾，並拿着擴音器回應訴求。他首先承諾，人文生態公園、殯儀館永遠不在文樓建設，鄉親父老不要因為這件事影響文樓鎮發展，引發現場一片歡呼聲。李偉華並指，現場律師及有關工作人員會為被捕者家屬辦理相關手續。<br />\n<br />\n化州市政府以建設文樓人文生態公園為名徵地，卻隱瞞會興建殯儀館及火葬場，事件曝光後，引發文樓鎮居民激烈反抗。上周四（28日），示威者擬到政府部門和平示威，卻遭大批防暴警封路阻攔，引發警民衝突。示威者斬樹或以竹枝架設路障，防止各路警力增援；他們又包圍特警，向他們投擲磚塊，並把增援的警車掀翻。不少手持木棍的民眾一度成功擊退鎮壓的特警，把他們趕上山，並把警方用來設置關卡的看守亭燒掉。不過，面對特警的精良裝備，以及不斷施放的催淚彈及水炮車，不少示威者都被打傷送院，當中包括老人和小孩。<br />\n<br />\n文樓鎮市民接連2天勇武對抗，估計約有200人被捕。血戰過後，當地氣氛稍為平靜，市面部份通道解封。不過鎮政府外的對峙卻未停止，大批民眾不分老小，齊齊高舉橫額、叫口號，與手持長盾的公安對峙，甚至有村民情緒激動下跪，提出五大訴求，包括停建火葬場、調查11月28日示威中警察濫權、釋放被捕人士、政府出資修建被毀財物，以及工程地點立即回復綠化。<br />\n<br />\n昨日，官方態度開始軟化，指將會釋放周四及周五的被捕人士，呼籲民眾回家。被捕村民在當日下午由兩架旅遊巴接載返鎮，民眾在道路上迎接他們，並拍掌叫好。但部份被捕者被「取保候審」，仍有可能被檢控。<br />\n <br />\n《蘋果》記者<br />\n-----------------------------<br />\n<br />\n【匿名港警爆大鑊】<br />\n韓國KBS時事節目《時事直擊：香港 被自殺》<br />\n一按即睇 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n【短片】【太太Victoria撐場】蘇兆輝季內首次起孖！「安賦」勝完再勝<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n【短片】【抗暴之戰】葵芳撞向人群交警已復工 鄧炳強盲撐：唔存在放縱仍積極調查"},{"pid":"4b06ecd686f5683022f7a9037c6e48b8ae75d763","tid":1764872,"uid":103981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:20:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港.......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a318758191741e660296cdc00250b4f069c7196e","tid":1764872,"uid":119984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:27:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"456ccdc81055fa82c9febc283f0564a90746be82","tid":1764872,"uid":302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:28:14.000Z","msg":"下 咁啲暴徒下次咪會得寸進尺？"},{"pid":"3a84e8f255df57713066344defc5beb6d0a66e80","tid":1764872,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:29:27.000Z","msg":"支那狗都好信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d6fab98d2868a005994ca75c9f7a7fad3ca54c9","tid":1764872,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:30:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.speakout.hk/港人觀點/48624/又是政府的錯-#selected\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.speakout.hk%2F%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E8%A7%80%E9%BB%9E%2F48624%2F%E5%8F%88%E6%98%AF%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%9A%84%E9%8C%AF-%23selected&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=d1d8ba80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.speakout.hk/港人觀點/48624/又是政府的錯-#selected</a><br />\n<br />\n係時候pin c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"399a8c8e3242cdc7c412b42d3efd664ea9015764","tid":1764872,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:31:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=28416653\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.discuss.com.hk%2Findex.php%3Faction%3Dthread%26tid%3D28416653&d=HsMqQMGMM0KOGi%2FJd%2BN0B2jFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=a40127e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.discuss.com.hk/index.php?action=thread&amp;tid=28416653</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af2dc0fe9e3aa4db05a5f51134be0323c47f0a25","tid":1764872,"uid":321050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T12:59:27.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位promote下。香港人贏唔贏靠尼個：<br />\n<br />\n非建制區議員平台<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.